## 8. Common Myths and Misunderstandings About AI

‚ùå AI thinks like humans  
‚ùå AI is always correct  
‚ùå AI replaces humans  

‚úÖ AI learns patterns  
‚úÖ AI assists humans  
‚úÖ AI depends on data quality  



## 9. The Road Ahead: The Future of AI

AI is moving toward **human-AI collaboration**.

Humans + AI
‚Üì
Better decisions
‚Üì
Higher productivity
‚Üì
Responsible and ethical AI

Future focus areas:
- Ethics and fairness
- Explainable AI
- Human-in-the-loop systems
- Personal AI assistants



## 10. Key Takeaways

- Traditional software follows rules; AI learns from data
- AI is the goal, ML is the method, GenAI is the creator
- AI evolved through multiple phases
- AI is already part of everyday life
- The future of AI is collaborative, not replacement-driven



